description: Deletes a model package. A model package is used to create SageMaker models or list on Amazon Web Services Marketplace. Buyers can subscribe to model packages listed on Amazon Web Services Marketplace to create models in SageMaker.

parameters.name: ModelPackageName
parameters.description: The name or Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model package to delete. When you specify a name, the name must have 1 to 63 characters. Valid characters are a-z, A-Z, 0-9, and - (hyphen).
